Shannon Carter has been jailed for three-and-a-half years for attacking Amelia Gledhill with a stiletto . 
  She repeatedly struck the 20-year-old with the shoe during a night out in Bradford . 
  The victim is said to have been traumatised and is still having problems with her eyesight . 
  The attack took place in a nightclub toilet after a row broke out between their friends . 
  Ms Carter followed her victim into the toilets after an argument in a bar . 
  She has been sentenced to three and a half years in jail at Bradford Crown Court . 
 